Privacy Policy for Opera GX Translator

Opera GX Translator does not collect, store, or share any personal data, including but not limited to location, browsing history, or personally identifiable information.

All translations are handled directly through Google Translate. This extension does not track user activity or send data to any external servers other than Google Translate when performing a translation request.

We are committed to respecting your privacy. No cookies, analytics, or trackers are included in this extension.

If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact Veil Interactive at:
https://github.com/VeilInteractive/Opera-GX-Translator

